{"tid":1727470,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"做事請跟從呢個《前線道德手冊》","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:17:26.000Z","uid":197235,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e572d3975ca393ce7207ddb82e3db4f4899835aa","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"我係中大有家長同我講，有好多時候都唔知前線做某樣事情嘅目的，<span style=\"color: red;\">希望有文宣可以說明一下</span>，佢仲話雖然唔割，但係有時都會有好反感，希望你哋做每樣野都係有目的同<span style=\"color: red;\">有合理加正當嘅理由</span>說服自己，再用呢個理由<span style=\"color: red;\">透過文宣說服其他人</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好做你最憎既人（曱甴）做既野</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>前線道德手冊</ins><br />\n<br />\n唔係要講道德，但係做嘢<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好一時衝動</span>，要對得住自己同手足，有錯請接受批評再改進，批評唔代表係割。（唔係話反對暴力同裝修啊）<br />\n<br />\n批評者<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以堅持自己係岩</span>，只係需要表達你自己既意見，一齊討論再作出決定，最重要語氣要好。<br />\n例如：屌你老母，做咩爆7仔，拎佢地D煙，係冇職員既情況下，有比錢唔係大哂架&mdash;＞可唔可以停手，我覺得唔應該咁樣做，因為佢唔係我哋裝修針對嘅對象，我哋唔應該為咗一已私欲破壞人哋啲嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係同你講民意，我係講我地都要尊重同關心家長心情同諗法，最低都要比佢哋知道我哋既諗法，物資唔係變出黎</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"95f4505fb25ef5643cf169a6ad363e8f6d16f604","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b145bdf0e6e5ebd4df1d7126140e6df2f96580","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ac4f015126188a9b746942128a1ea5337fcffe5","tid":1727470,"uid":335348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:39:57.000Z","msg":"民意好緊要<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726209/page/1</a><br />\n深度分析，大家可以幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457cbe03a02dd33badd1431765d389fb38f9d687","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"7仔單野我估大家都知我講咩"},{"pid":"18486a6011010c884e807a55643ba3293423e378","tid":1727470,"uid":306592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"457cbe03a02dd33badd1431765d389fb38f9d687","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"7仔單野我估大家都知我講咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:41:47.000Z","msg":"呢單真心覺得唔係太好"},{"pid":"c67c30ef8411a88b485b8034420c407ee55b5e26","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1700b0b881ff5e201208ae7f5b6f3d8ea90106db","tid":1727470,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c9198cd2347b7bc230319e0ed4fb77f7d3dde7","tid":1727470,"uid":293947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"小心已開此出現群眾鬥群眾的情況,正中中共下懷,可能自編自道一次殺警,或警察家屬)仲要扮到好名顯兇手來自某群體例如大學,然後令POPO信以為真或者有份道演)再攻大學,中間選民一系唔投票,一系改投建制,(以上如有雷同,實屬不幸),因此請大家忍耐理性及保持最高警覺,緊手道德底線."}]}